description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '20 MIN BEGINNER FLEXIBILITY ROUTINE (Stretches for the Inflexible)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Not flexible? Follow along with this 20 min stretch routine designed to help increase flexibility! Great for beginner's or anyone in need of a great stretch!
